00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:07.510 align:start position:0%
Structured Query Language, SQL, ba chutu kori kole SQL, relational database management system or loge joga-jog goribar ek gold standard basa.

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:11.270 align:start position:0%
Tumi hoito MySQL, Postgres, Microsoft SQL Server, ar Oracle'or motor database'or kotha huniso.

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:17.349 align:start position:0%
E bakkun SQL'or uore banano, kintu tarar nijor alok alok bodol ase.

00:00:17.359 --> 00:00:24.790 align:start position:0%
Idore poila 1970'or dosok'ot IBM'or System R database twe data bodolabar ar anibar jonno bona hoisilo.

00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:31.109 align:start position:0%
1986 shal'ot, idore ekta standard syntax banai deya hoisilo, jede aji-o technical kaj'ot boro beshi popular.

00:00:31.119 --> 00:00:37.430 align:start position:0%
Ek relational database, data're table'ot sajei, Excel spreadsheet'or motori, jene column'ot thage attribute ba data'r doron.

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:41.990 align:start position:0%
Aar hodok row, ek ekta alok record bujei, jar nijor ekta unique ID thage.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:46.229 align:start position:0%
Idore 'primary key' koi. Amra data point'or maj'ot somporko boned parir.

00:00:46.239 --> 00:00:50.950 align:start position:0%
Ek row'or unique ID're loi, arek table'or alok row'ot dori diye.

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:58.790 align:start position:0%
Ere 'foreign key' namor ek special column'ot rakhe. Jemon, 'teams' table'ot 'team_id' primary key, kintu 'players' table'ot he 'foreign key'.

00:00:58.800 --> 00:01:02.950 align:start position:0%
E data structure're amake bujei je, ekjon player ek team'ot bhag,

00:01:02.960 --> 00:01:11.510 align:start position:0%
kintu ek team'ot bhek player thaged pare. Ene gori amra data're duplication ar redundancy komabar jonno tar sorba-chutu normal form'ot sajeir.

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:21.749 align:start position:0%
Ehon SQL'or kam khali data pora, bona, bodola, ba dila no, borong tarar moddhor somporko hisebe data're ek loge join gora bhi.

00:01:21.759 --> 00:01:28.390 align:start position:0%
Tar syntax'ot kisu main ongso ase. Ek 'statement' hosse ek code'or tukura je database'or uore kam gore.

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:36.870 align:start position:0%
Statement'or bitore 'keyword' thage. Jemon, 'SELECT' di, tumi je column sa, tar query gored pariba.

00:01:36.880 --> 00:01:43.910 align:start position:0%
Column ar table'or nam're 'identifier' koi. Kintu amra hoito hodo row nesair.

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:49.429 align:start position:0%
Henge, 'WHERE' keyword di result'ore filter gori, khali he record'un anibar jonno je kisu sorto mane.

00:01:49.439 --> 00:01:57.109 align:start position:0%
Ida table'or hodok row'or uore sai, ar jegun'ot sorto'ti 'true' hoi, hegun're query't anei.

00:01:57.119 --> 00:02:03.590 align:start position:0%
Tarpor amra hoito 'JOIN' keyword di, ekkere alok table'or data're jura di parir, ek table'or primary key'or loge arek table'or foreign key're mil gori.

00:02:03.600 --> 00:02:12.390 align:start position:0%
Amra je bonelir, he hosse kisu 'clause'or somosti, jegun mili ek pura SQL statement bone. Ehon amra e code're sate sate SQL-supported database'ot saled parir.

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:15.990 align:start position:0%
Ida silo 100 second'ot Structured Query Language.

